'''The onion router''', or [::Tor], is a software package that allows you to use an anonymity network to keep secret the details of your Internet activity.

* http://www.torproject.org/
* [[WikiPedia:Tor (anonymity network)]]
* [https://wiki.torproject.org/noreply/TheOnionRouter TorProject:TheOnionRouter]

[[Anonymous]] editors of the Wiki can use this tool to keep their IP address secret.  See UserName for more information.
